message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This item has been meticulously designed and crafted to meet your highest standards. It's worth $15,000 to us, but considering its exceptional quality and the value it would bring to you, we're offering it to you at an exclusive price of $14,000. We believe this is a fantastic opportunity for both of us to benefit from this extraordinary product. Please let me know if you have any questions or if you'd like to proceed with the purchase.
